STATE of Louisiana
v.
Huey RANDOLPH NO. 2018-KH-1180 Supreme Court of Louisiana. May 20, 2019

Denied. Applicant has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing. State ex rel. Randolph v. State, 16-2170 (La. 3/2/18), 237 So.3d 497.
